OL,3,CFormer Pakistan Prime Minister jailed
OL,4,Cfor 17 years for selling state gifts
OL,6,FA court in Pakistan has sentenced
OL,7,Fformer Prime Minister Imran Khan and
OL,8,Fhis wife, Bushra Bibi, to 17 years in
OL,9,Fprison for selling and retaining state
OL,10,Fgifts.
OL,12,FThe couple kept and sold the gifts,
OL,13,Fincluding jewellery from Saudi Arabia,
OL,14,Fat prices far below market value while
OL,15,FKhan was in office.
OL,17,FBoth pleaded not guilty when they were
OL,18,Findicted last year.
