OL,3,CFormer Pakistan Prime Minister jailed
OL,4,Cfor 17 years for selling state gifts
OL,6,FUnder Pakistani law, government
OL,7,Fofficials and politicians can keep
OL,8,Fgifts received from foreign
OL,9,Fdignitaries, if they buy them at the
OL,10,Fassessed market value and declare any
OL,11,Fproceeds earned from selling them.
OL,13,FProsecutors said Khan and Bibi
OL,14,Fdeclared the value of the gifts at
OL,15,Fjust over #8,755 ($10,000), far below
OL,16,Fthe actual market value of #213,446
OL,17,F($285,521).
OL,19,FThat allowed them to purchase the
OL,20,Fitems at a reduced price.
