OL,3,CFormer Pakistan Prime Minister jailed
OL,4,Cfor 17 years for selling state gifts
OL,6,FKhan's spokesperson, Zulfiquar
OL,7,FBukhari, said the verdict in the graft
OL,8,Fcase ignored basic principles of
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,FIn a statement, he said that the
OL,12,F"criminal liability was imposed
OL,13,Fwithout proof of intent, gain, or
OL,14,Floss, relying instead on a
OL,15,Fretrospective reinterpretation of
OL,16,Frules".
