OL,3,CFormer Pakistan Prime Minister jailed
OL,4,Cfor 17 years for selling state gifts
OL,6,FBukhari said the court ruling "raised
OL,7,Fserious questions about the fairness
OL,8,Fand impartiality of the process,
OL,9,Fturning justice into a tool for
OL,10,Fselective prosecution".
OL,12,FBut Khan's opposition Pakistan Tehreek-
OL,13,Fe-Insaf party denounced the verdict in
OL,14,Fa statement, calling it "a black
OL,15,Fchapter in history".
OL,17,FKhan was present in the court when the
OL,18,Fjudge announced the verdict in the
OL,19,FAdiala prison in the city of
OL,20,FRawalpindi.
