OL,3,CFormer Pakistan Prime Minister jailed
OL,4,Cfor 17 years for selling state gifts
OL,6,FKhan has faced multiple prison terms
OL,7,Fsince 2023 on corruption and other
OL,8,Fcharges, which the former cricket star
OL,9,Fand his supporters have alleged are
OL,10,Faimed at blocking his political career.
OL,12,FThe 73-year-old was ousted in a no-
OL,13,Fconfidence vote in April 2022.
OL,15,FHis party remains in opposition in the
OL,16,Fparliament.
